24:01.037 --> 24:04.239
I came two minutes
before you here...

24:04.273 --> 24:07.509
And four minutes earlier.

24:07.543 --> 24:12.514
Well, that may have been a function
of etiquette as much as biology.

24:12.548 --> 24:16.852
Ladies first?
You are a gentleman.

24:18.369 --> 24:21.390
A hungry gentleman.

24:21.424 --> 24:24.536
Maybe we should get a bite...
go for dinner somewhere.

24:33.202 --> 24:34.703
Masters.

24:34.737 --> 24:38.306
I was hoping you were
already on your way, daddy.

24:38.341 --> 24:42.811
<i>We decided this morning to have
an evening to ourselves. Remember?</i>

24:42.845 --> 24:45.265
Of course.

24:45.266 --> 24:49.584
- Uh, I should be leaving shortly.
- All right.

24:49.619 --> 24:51.787
Drive fast...
not too fast.

24:52.320 --> 24:54.624
I will do both.

25:00.238 --> 25:04.608
I just realized...
I was due home an hour ago.

25:10.273 --> 25:12.574
Uh, you're unzipped.
Here. Let me.

25:12.608 --> 25:15.343
Oh, I'll get it.
Good night.

25:53.733 --> 25:55.911
Barton?

25:57.086 --> 25:58.672
What the hell?

25:59.039 --> 26:00.889
I was robbed.

26:00.923 --> 26:04.675
- Why aren't you at emergency?
- It's not serious.

26:10.266 --> 26:13.778
Lie down.
Come on. Lie down.

26:17.865 --> 26:21.076
The train didn't leave for an hour.

26:21.110 --> 26:29.443
I had time to kill. So I... I parked
behind those theaters on Market Street.

26:29.531 --> 26:32.594
I mean,
it's not a bad neighborhood.

26:32.655 --> 26:34.927
I figured I'd use the time to...

26:36.592 --> 26:38.593
...Plan my trip.

26:38.628 --> 26:45.184
When out of nowhere, these hoodlums
walk up to my car with a knife.

26:45.348 --> 26:46.981
And for absolutely no reason...

26:46.996 --> 26:50.520
For god's sake, Barton.
I know why you're not at the hospital.

26:50.611 --> 26:53.679
I know why there are no police
here asking questions.

26:53.753 --> 26:57.297
So just say nothing if you want,
but don't lie to me.

26:58.794 --> 27:03.063
- People can't know about this.
- Obviously.

27:03.098 --> 27:06.965
- I could lose my family.
- You could lose everything.

27:07.230 --> 27:11.466
You <i>will</i> lose everything...
If you carry on like this...

27:11.907 --> 27:16.710
Your job, your reputation,
your medical license.

27:16.745 --> 27:21.421
Is it worth it, just to meet
some boy in an alley?

27:23.351 --> 27:26.687
Everything you've spent
a lifetime building for yourself...

27:26.721 --> 27:29.535
For this university?

27:30.058 --> 27:34.286
You think Margaret
and Vivian will stand by you...

27:34.738 --> 27:36.564
When this all comes out?

27:36.598 --> 27:38.833
It's not going to come out.

27:38.834 --> 27:42.292
You nearly got killed tonight,
Barton, For sitting in a car.

27:49.307 --> 27:51.142
You can do your shirt up.

27:58.920 --> 28:02.723
- I can go again.
- See, I like that about you.

28:02.757 --> 28:05.303
You get on top this time.

28:23.532 --> 28:26.768
Austin, someone's coming.

28:26.802 --> 28:28.236
Would that someone be you?

28:28.271 --> 28:33.241
No, Austin,
there's someone in the driveway.

28:33.276 --> 28:35.517
Who is it?

28:36.112 --> 28:37.779
My husband.

28:45.054 --> 28:49.024
Margaret, I'm sorry.
Did I wake you?

28:49.058 --> 28:51.126
I was up.
I wasn't expecting you.

28:51.160 --> 28:54.596
The train, a problem
with the track and, uh...

28:54.630 --> 28:57.295
Anyway, New York is off.

28:59.089 --> 29:00.723
What's wrong, dear?

29:08.068 --> 29:11.657
I need you to go to your
bedroom, Barton, and stay there.

29:13.261 --> 29:15.134
Please.

29:40.810 --> 29:45.880
<i>Forward. And back.
Now up. And down.</i>

29:45.915 --> 29:48.049
<i>One and two.</i>

29:48.084 --> 29:50.552
<i>Three and four.</i>

29:52.521 --> 29:54.489
<i>Forward and back.</i>

29:54.523 --> 29:58.108
- I'm sorry I'm...
- There he is.

29:58.221 --> 30:02.098
The very man who bought me
my first Martini.

30:02.113 --> 30:05.433
Remember?
Majestic ballroom?

30:07.203 --> 30:10.839
You danced
to the Lester Lanin band.

30:13.275 --> 30:14.709
I was 27.

30:15.648 --> 30:18.446
Would have climbed
the Matterhorn to impress you.

30:18.481 --> 30:20.899
You didn't have to, did you?

30:29.091 --> 30:34.427
Just a hint of vermouth,
